   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" title="Jon Sterling" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>31</fr:day></fr:date><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <html:p>Fixing <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b:B]]></fr:tex>, we must check that the <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001Q/" title="Fiber" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001Q/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001Q" type="local">fiber</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001H/" title="Contractible type" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001H/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001H" type="local">contractible</fr:link>. For the centre of contraction, we must construct an element of this <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001Q/" title="Fiber" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001Q/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001Q" type="local">fiber</fr:link>; because <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001T/" title="n-truncated map" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001T/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001T" type="local">propositional</fr:link> by <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0048/" title="embeddings are propositional" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0048/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0048" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0048/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0048" /></fr:link>, the <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001Q/" title="Fiber" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001Q/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001Q" type="local">fiber</fr:link> is a <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" title="Proposition" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>, so it suffices by the induction principle for <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0028/" title="Propositional truncation" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0028/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0028" type="local">propositional truncation</fr:link> to observe that the <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001Q/" title="Fiber" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001Q/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-001Q" type="local">fiber</fr:link> is <html:em>inhabited</html:em> because <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0029/" title="Surjection" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0029/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0029" type="local">surjective</fr:link>.</html:p>
