   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" title="Jon Sterling" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>31</fr:day></fr:date><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <html:p>This is immediate, using the unit map of <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0028/" title="Propositional truncation" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0028/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-0028" type="local">propositional truncation</fr:link> and the <fr:link href="/foreign/erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000U/" title="Biinverse" uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000U/" display-uri="https://erct.jonmsterling.com/erct-000U" type="local">section</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
